{"tid":1956872,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"針對最近分化風氣應對方法","createTime":"2020-04-03T13:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:19:05.000Z","uid":137291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"810e9523fa3fbce6a4a35e4a038ecb42c4794f77","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"相信大家最近都見到好多分化po或者topic<br />\n搞到好多人都好迷茫(包括我)<br />\n最近係多到令我懷疑係咪對家分化我地<br />\n所以我正式宣布<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">除非有FC曬嘅證據 e.g. 對話 錄音 影片 數etc.</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後唔好信匿名投稿<br />\n淨係信有信用度嘅人(或者鋪頭)嘅資訊<br />\n如果有手足要匿名搞稿請搵呢啲人/鋪頭幫手出聲</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有信用度嘅定義係乜? 點解要咁做?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. fc過公認真係幫過手足 e.g.請手足 助養 車隊<br />\n2. 透明度高嘅鋪頭 e.g.會寫曬捐款點用   收入捐去邊</span></span></strong> (sorry所以部分做地下活動嘅商戶唔包括在內)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3. 有做過實事幫手足 e.g.出事俾手足匿入去鋪頭   仲要幫手頂住</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔好屌製造大台住<br />\n要贏始終需要一定程度嘅方向<br />\n我地唔要一個大台   但係分開好多值得信嘅人就得</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁做至少可以令到大家冇咁迷茫<br />\n同埋大概有個方向點樣行落去<br />\n我地討厭嘅係同我地割席   叫我地死開嘅大台<br />\n分清楚大台同埋有公信力嘅人<br />\n我地始終要一定程度同埋數量有公信力嘅人先可以更簡單行落去<br />\n不割席不分化不篤灰"},{"pid":"c821c7fc9b41640ce825f0b6be5bcdc2b84e5a3d","tid":1956872,"uid":203397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"強姦，無可疑論點fc?<br />\n<br />\n有啲野無定義，得個人道德指標<br />\n讀者自行決定，無咩問題<br />\n唔算係分化"},{"pid":"d1ec87c4e2f67dea8cec06191459fba0be436a74","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c821c7fc9b41640ce825f0b6be5bcdc2b84e5a3d","tid":1956872,"uid":203397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"強姦，無可疑論點fc?<br />\n<br />\n有啲野無定義，得個人道德指標<br />\n讀者自行決定，無咩問題<br />\n唔算係分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:16:47.000Z","msg":"我意思係人血饅頭嗰啲"},{"pid":"f532c88f364e8f39327488efe4c4076d48cbe2c7","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c821c7fc9b41640ce825f0b6be5bcdc2b84e5a3d","tid":1956872,"uid":203397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"強姦，無可疑論點fc?<br />\n<br />\n有啲野無定義，得個人道德指標<br />\n讀者自行決定，無咩問題<br />\n唔算係分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"強姦呢啲緊係唔洗fc<br />\n已成事實"},{"pid":"8d97b2bb39d00026feaef7dc28043f521699f379","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c821c7fc9b41640ce825f0b6be5bcdc2b84e5a3d","tid":1956872,"uid":203397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"強姦，無可疑論點fc?<br />\n<br />\n有啲野無定義，得個人道德指標<br />\n讀者自行決定，無咩問題<br />\n唔算係分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:17:59.000Z","msg":"講緊最近大量分化po<br />\n喺度分化黃店   分化部分有少少知名度嘅人<br />\n唔包括警暴嘅嘢   嗰啲嘢唔洗fc都知係真"},{"pid":"c7dc312a31ce67ed06b1513738e35a641449c10c","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4322dee947ca6da1a9a05c7052e8978e3795efa2","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:18:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e8138ea09ca9140106468a9608490dec8ab4403","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cec00e06584387496e76d1f7cea3e7e4d8aa1156","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5bf0a6fa739a1dc47357a5132a59ccd33fe12ab","tid":1956872,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}